useEffect :
It is called using a call back function and a dependency array.
call back function is mandatory, dependency array is optional.

The call back method is called after every render of the component if depedency array is not given.
Dependency array is used to control the behaviour of useEffect.

3 cases:
i) When no dependency array is given, the function is called after each component render.
ii) When empty dependency array is given, the function is called after initial render.
iii) When depedency array is given some value/ object, the function is called only when the values/ objects changed.

